## Troubleshooting

> [!TIP]
> **Agent not firing?** Check the trigger D&R rule is enabled, then verify the agent's debounce/suppression key hasn't locked it out.

> [!TIP]
> **Agent timing out?** Check the TTL setting. If the agent consistently runs out of time, increase the TTL in the hive configuration.

> [!TIP]
> **Budget exceeded?** Each agent has a `max_budget_usd` cap. If the agent hits its budget, the session terminates. Check AI session logs.

